@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4 text-primary">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p class="text-muted">Last Updated: @DateTime.Now.ToString("MMMM dd, yyyy")</p>

    <p>
        At <strong>Star Events</strong>, your privacy is our top priority.
        This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information
        when you use our website, mobile applications, and event-related services.
        By accessing or using our services, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-5">1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, billing and payment details when you register, book tickets, or contact us.</li>
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Login credentials, preferences, and saved event details.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> IP address, device information, browser type, and access times when you visit our website.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies & Tracking Technologies:</strong> To personalize content, remember preferences, and analyze site traffic.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-5">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>Your information is used for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>To process bookings, payments, and event registrations.</li>
        <li>To send confirmations, service updates, and important notifications.</li>
        <li>To provide customer support and respond to inquiries.</li>
        <li>To personalize user experience and improve our services.</li>
        <li>To send promotional offers, newsletters, and marketing communications (only if you have opted in).</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations and prevent fraudulent activity.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-5">3. How We Share Your Information</h3>
    <p>
        We respect your privacy and do <strong>not sell or rent</strong> your personal information.
        However, we may share limited data with:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Such as payment processors, IT support, and marketing tools to deliver our services effectively.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Authorities:</strong> If required by law, court order, or to prevent fraud or abuse.</li>
        <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In case of a merger, acquisition, or asset sale, your data may be transferred as part of the business assets.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-5">4. Data Security</h3>
    <p>
        We implement strict security measures to protect your personal information,
        including encryption, secure servers, and access controls.
        However, please note that no method of internet transmission or storage is completely secure.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-5">5. Your Rights & Choices</h3>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access, update, or correct your personal information.</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your account and data, subject to legal requirements.</li>
        <li>Opt out of promotional communications at any time via unsubscribe links or account settings.</li>
        <li>Restrict or object to data processing in certain circumstances.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-5">6. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h3>
    <p>
        We use cookies and similar technologies to improve website functionality and user experience.
        You may disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features of our site may not function properly.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-5">7. Third-Party Links</h3>
    <p>
        Our website may contain links to third-party websites.
        We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external sites.
        Please review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-5">8. Data Retention</h3>
    <p>
        We retain your personal data only as long as necessary to provide our services
        and fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required by law.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-5">9. International Data Transfers</h3>
    <p>
        If you access our services from outside Sri Lanka, please note that your information may be transferred
        and stored in countries with different data protection laws.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-5">10. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
    <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
        Any changes will be posted on this page with a revised "Last Updated" date.
        Continued use of our services after changes indicates acceptance of the updated policy.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-5">11. Contact Us</h3>
    <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@starevents.com">privacy@starevents.com</a></li>
        <li>Phone: +94 XXX XXX XXXX</li>
        <li>Address: Star Events, Colombo, Sri Lanka</li>
    </ul>
</div>
